<div class="credit first">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p>crossover：《远方（loner）》，本文部分内容改编自游戏内容。<br />
挑战：<br />
1.整好活；<br />
2.来了，走了，我的一生结束了；<br />
3.超速行驶。<br />
本文作者为<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/raintree" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5375092); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5375092&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663828" alt="RainTree" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5375092)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/raintree" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5375092); return false;">RainTree</a></span>。该作者的更多作品见<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/there-is-a-man-named-rain">Rain，似乎是个研究员。</a><br />
图片来源：<a href="https://i.loli.net/2020/03/20/mu1Ms2v3lrLEp8O.jpg">https://i.loli.net/2020/03/20/mu1Ms2v3lrLEp8O.jpg</a>，由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/miku393" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2996561); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2996561&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663828" alt="miku393" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2996561)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/miku393" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2996561); return false;">miku393</a></span>上传至画廊。<br />
均遵守CC协议。</p>
<p>鸣谢：感谢<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-obsidian-shard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5090298); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5090298&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663828" alt="The Obsidian Shard" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5090298)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-obsidian-shard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5090298); return false;">The Obsidian Shard</a></span>前辈在写作过程中对我的指导。</p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div class="creditBottomRate" style="position:relative;height:30px;">
<div style="text-align: center; top: 0px;"><div class="page-rate-widget-box"><span class="rate-points">评分:&nbsp;<span class="number prw54353">+33</span></span><span class="rateup btn btn-default"><a title="我喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, 1)">+</a></span><span class="ratedown btn btn-default"><a title="我不喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, -1)">&#8211;</a></span><span class="cancel btn btn-default"><a title="取消我的投票" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.cancelVote(event)">x</a></span></div></div>
